{"tid":895034,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人覺得過馬路應該分左右人流？","createTime":"2018-11-09T00:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-09T03:02:34.000Z","uid":104171,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"56cbae35337469eda668bdd40e787d7318e00ad1","tid":895034,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T00:39:48.000Z","msg":"過馬路見到對面啲人一字排開咁款<br />\n一綠燈就一字排開咁行過黎<br />\n兩班人流炒埋一堆撞哂<br />\n完全係混亂！<br />\n<br />\n應該每邊路邊只有一半可以企人<br />\n過路處就左右劃分「去」同「返」<br />\n「去」同「返」喺過馬路嘅時候就唔會炒埋一碟<br />\n咁樣行得暢順好多<br />\n亦唔洗浪費精力同時間去避人"},{"pid":"5de4ae6499c681d3d3b821b7bfe9bb3d586f0339","tid":895034,"uid":195364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T00:48:29.000Z","msg":"分左分右由你開始"},{"pid":"07ba2a0acb142bfc48858a9df43d2cc94c439a41","tid":895034,"uid":82397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T01:29:45.000Z","msg":"得一半企人應該塞到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而行人路要好似馬路咁劃慢中快線<br />\n費事有啲人行得慢嘅阻住成條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bc7d0e5d76dd655d0ae195f6b16ed3118db0697","tid":895034,"uid":104171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-09T03:02:34.000Z","msg":"原本大家對沖可能仲塞"}]}